Package com.fhkiel.oopproject.model

package com.fhkiel.oopproject.model
contains all data model for the characters
  • Class Summary
    Class
    Description
    Character
    Class-Description:
    Abstract class for all characters providing methods for name matching and updating
    LordOfRingsChar
    Class-Description:
    The class "LordOfRingsChar" is a concrete childclass of the abstract Character and represents Characters from the LotR-Universe.
    StarWarsChar
    Class-Description:
    The class "StarWarsChar" is a concrete childclass of the abstract Character and representsffjdk Characters from the Star-Wars-Universe.
    UpdateVisitor
    Class-Description:
    The UpdateVisitor-Class automatically differentiate between the two concrete classes and perfomes the updateprocess of these classes.
